Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.50,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,我出發了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.16,0:21:08.30,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,你們覺得她會來嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.75,0:21:09.85,Dial-CH,,0,0,0,,應該會吧
